---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy – AngloEdge" description="Our privacy policy and how we handle your data.">
  <div class="max-w-prose mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Introduction</h2>
    <p>
      AngloEdge ("we", "us", "our") operates the angloedge.com website (the "Site"). This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Site and the choices you have associated with that data.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Information Collection and Use</h2>
    <p>
      We collect several different types of information for various purposes to provide and improve our service to you.
    </p>

    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-navy mt-6 mb-3">Types of Data Collected:</h3>
    <ul class="ml-6 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Cookie Data:</strong> We use cookies to enhance your experience. You can instruct your browser to refuse cookies or alert you when cookies are being sent.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We may collect information about how the Site is accessed and used (e.g., the pages you visit, time spent on pages).</li>
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> If you subscribe to our newsletter or contact us, we collect your email address.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Use of Data</h2>
    <p>
      AngloEdge uses the collected data for various purposes:
    </p>
    <ul class="ml-6 space-y-2">
      <li>To provide and maintain the Site</li>
      <li>To notify you about changes to our Site</li>
      <li>To allow you to participate in interactive features of our Site</li>
      <li>To provide analysis or valuable information so that we can improve the Site</li>
      <li>To monitor the usage of the Site</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      We use cookies for:
    </p>
    <ul class="ml-6 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for the Site to function properly (e.g., cookie consent preference)</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Help us understand how users interact with the Site (only with your consent)</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-4">
      You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect Site functionality.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      We may use third-party services for analytics and to help us understand Site usage:
    </p>
    <ul class="ml-6 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> To track and analyze Site traffic (with consent)</li>
      <li><strong>RSS Feeds:</strong> Your RSS reader may collect data about feed subscriptions</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
      Depending on your location, you have the following rights:
    </p>
    <ul class="ml-6 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Right to Access:</strong> Request what data we hold about you</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your data</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Rectification:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Opt-Out:</strong> Withdraw consent for data processing at any time</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
    <p>
      The security of your data is important to us. We use HTTPS encryption for data transmission, but no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at:
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4">
      <strong>AngloEdge</strong><br />
      <a href="https://x.com/angloedgee" class="text-navy hover:underline">@angloedgee on X</a>
    </p>

    <hr class="my-8" />

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-8">
      This privacy policy conforms to GDPR (EU General Data Protection Regulation) requirements for EU users and similar privacy legislation in other jurisdictions.
    </p>

    <a href="/" class="inline-block mt-8 text-navy hover:underline">← Back to home</a>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  h2 {
    @apply font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4;
  }

  h3 {
    @apply font-serif text-xl font-bold text-navy mt-6 mb-3;
  }

  p {
    @apply leading-tight text-gray-900 mb-4;
  }

  ul {
    @apply ml-6 space-y-2 mb-4;
  }

  li {
    @apply leading-tight text-gray-900;
  }

  a {
    @apply text-navy hover:underline;
  }

  hr {
    @apply border-gray-200;
  }
</style>
